      "span_text": "Reverse transcription (RT) was performed using Moloney murine leukemia virus reverse transcriptase (Promega) with the primer 3ЈUTRDX-R (Table 1 ) specifically annealing to the 3Ј-untranslated region (UTR) of repPAC-␤gal but not to the 3Ј-UTR of C20Dxrepneo [CITATION_1] ."
